gText_Birch_Welcome::
        .string "Hello there! Welcome to the world of POKéMON!\p"
        .string "My name is BIRCH.\p"
        .string "But everyone calls me the POKéMON\n"
        .string "PROFESSOR.\p"
        .string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon::
        .string "This world is inhabited far and wide by\n"
        .string "creatures called POKéMON.\p"
        .string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech::
        .string "For some people, POKéMON are pets.\p"
        .string "Others use them for battling.\p"
        .string "As for myself... I study POKéMON as a\n"
        .string "profession.\p"
        .string "...Huh? Wait a minute...\p"
        .string "You... You look familiar...\n"
        .string "Have we met before?\p"
        .string "...No, it couldn't be...\p"
        .string "Are you... could you be the child who\n"
        .string "lived in LITTLEROOT years ago?\p"
        .string "$"

gText_Birch_AndYouAre::
        .string "$"

gText_Birch_BoyOrGirl::
        .string "$"

gText_Birch_WhatsYourName::
        .string "Ah, so you're a {STR_VAR_1}. Got it.\p"
        .string "What's your name?$"

gText_Birch_SoItsPlayer::
        .string "Right, your name is {PLAYER}.\p"
        .string "That's a name I haven't heard in years.$"

gText_Birch_YourePlayer::
        .string "You left HOENN eight years ago...\n"
        .string "and now you're finally back!\p"
        .string "BRENDAN and MAY will be thrilled.\p"
        .string "They still talk about you sometimes.\p"
        .string "Even though so much has changed...\n"
        .string "something tells me you're about to\n"
        .string "change everything even more.\p"
        .string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
        .string "Your adventure is just beginning.\p"
        .string "I'll see you in LITTLEROOT TOWN!\p"
        .string "$"
